  sci-libs/libsingular: bump to a version that can compile against ntl[threads]

  31 Jan 2016; François Bissey <francois.bissey@canterbury.ac.nz> metadata.xml:
  sci-libs/libsingular: update metadata

  27 Jan 2016; François Bissey <francois.bissey@canterbury.ac.nz>
  libsingular-3.1.7_p1-r6.ebuild:
  sci-libs/libsingular: depend on ntl[-threads]

  23 Jan 2016; François Bissey <francois.bissey@canterbury.ac.nz>
  files/singular-3.1.3.3-dylib.patch, files/singular-3.1.3.3-soname.patch,
  libsingular-3.1.7_p1-r6.ebuild:
  sci-libs/libsingular: move to EAPI 6

