*libsingular-3.1.6-r3 (21 Jul 2014)

  21 Jul 2014; François Bissey <francois.bissey@canterbury.ac.nz>
  +files/singular-3.1.6-fix_mpoly_factor_segfault.patch,
  +files/singular-3.1.6-flintconfig.patch, +libsingular-3.1.6-r3.ebuild,
  -libsingular-3.1.6-r2.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  flint enabled libsingular with a few extra patches from sage. sage 6.3.beta6
  requires a flint enabled libsingular and will destroy  quite a few patches to
  module-list.py in the process so be patient, it is coming slowly.

